---
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<Header />

<main style="max-width: 800px; margin: 60px auto; padding: 20px;">
  <h1>IR Signal Capture & Replay System</h1>

  <p>
    Designed and implemented an interrupt-driven IR signal capture and replay
    system using a PIC18 microcontroller. The system measures pulse timing
    using hardware timers and reproduces signals using PWM modules.
  </p>

  <h2>Hardware Setup</h2>
  <img
    src="/images/ir-setup.jpg"
    alt="IR hardware setup"
    style="max-width: 600px; width: 100%; border-radius: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px;"
  />

  <h2>Technical Highlights</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Interrupt-driven signal capture</li>
    <li>Timer configuration and prescaler calculation</li>
    <li>PWM-based signal reproduction</li>
    <li>Low-power sleep mode optimization</li>
    <li>Datasheet-driven peripheral configuration</li>
  </ul>

  <p>
    <a
      href="https://github.com/JAMES-DIMARCO/JAMES-DIMARCO.github.io"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener noreferrer"
    >
      View GitHub Repository
    </a>
  </p>
</main>

<Footer />
